author: By KATHY McCORMACK and HOLLY RAMER
title: New Hampshire seeks volunteers, stay-at-home order resisted
description: CONCORD, N.H. (AP) — New Hampshire is seeking volunteers, both medical and non-medical, who can help deal with surging cases of the new coronavirus in the state.
content:
